{"tid":1424633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改革不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:51:50.000Z","uid":271381,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23ec5f7ee049b63b267038cd0af161664464ec94","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"不合作運動無論如何一定會影響市民<br />\n並會造成一定程度嘅反感<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但不合作活動絕對有用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n與其單單停止<br />\n不如<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">稍為更改形式</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n例如港鐵不合作以每站阻門5次代表5大訴求<br />\n阻塞主要道路改為限一線行車<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔阻日常返工但增加返工成本</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">令市民雖作出應對措施 增加對政治關注</span></span>"},{"pid":"e854a9ff720e32d966d990c2a1a4117dce752483","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ef9b744b12f5c4ebd3562b728f762aa29f9b3ad9","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9f67d65ff3ce810d302235c3a361a52506ca5579","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"cd083bd4629fc77682b963a7b82cecfa72701785","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"24c3079a0ca03bb61b7b5b0980c0eaaa2845728f","tid":1424633,"uid":271381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"3e7c4a7741da419bfd6fa0a43247b52a1f55c8be","tid":1424633,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"打交可以 唔好打臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\